# Ontology-level metadata (title, description, license, creators, citation,
# created, source, IAO:0000700 roots) now lives in aio-edit.owl, which is the
# ODK edit file whose ontology annotations reach the release. This file is
# applied to the ROBOT-template component (components/aio-component.owl) and
# intentionally carries no ontology annotations, to avoid duplicating or
# conflicting with the edit file. See issue #171.
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
